  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-01",
      "markerIndex": 0,
      "replayStartSec": 2.421292,
      "replayEndSec": 9.419365,
      "narrationText": "让我们以 env 模式设置第一个密钥。该值会作为环境变量落入容器内。注意那个空的 current 标志，我们在声明这是一个全新密钥，没有先前的值。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-01.9b5f9eae.mp3",
      "textHash": "9b5f9eae9ed8df31f82cc7d3d8d05df50f84ae84190d3ff68039a448a1ca25b0",
      "audioDurationSec": 15.882449,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-01-after.db2fb05b.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.04898,
      "afterTextHash": "db2fb05b8ac13b2a73ab055dc71d14f70b8d40336ff9686cb889fced2dd90a34"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 9.419365,
      "replayEndSec": 16.481794,
      "narrationText": "现在设置一个 file 模式密钥。file 模式永远不会将值放入容器的环境变量，而是使用 Docker 的标准密钥机制将其写入斜杠 run 斜杠 secrets 下的文件。敏感内容优先选择这种模式。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-02.f44274d7.mp3",
      "textHash": "f44274d7ccf87e9b9732c0f75c7fcb16e6001f85a8f2825e6901b50af8a315ce",
      "audioDurationSec": 18.520816,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-02-after.ce03262b.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 6.426122,
      "afterTextHash": "ce03262bfb86a0f52e22c7ce646e9c894532a36cd99829a6977c3cbe7b8fad19"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 16.481794,
      "replayEndSec": 20.7282,
      "narrationText": "让我们列出已有的密钥。只显示名称和模式，无论谁来查询，列表永远不会显示值。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-03.7fb44232.mp3",
      "textHash": "7fb442322d75c56737ae87b2e79c3d743c6e001e54a02507ad2cb3ce5d9a3466",
      "audioDurationSec": 8.280816,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-03-after.19035a3f.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.160816,
      "afterTextHash": "19035a3fdfea5049205b3a1a243d57412079248ba14fc669cdc1392e33e89f46"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 20.7282,
      "replayEndSec": 25.737687,
      "narrationText": "这里是让人意外的部分。get 返回的是摘要，而不是值。没有任何标志能让它返回明文，也没有任何命令能给你拿回密钥值。这就是 GitHub Actions 模型：设计上只写不读。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-04.7d0ef271.mp3",
      "textHash": "7d0ef271dd57360aed653d59306a37cc599a47a530a4ee14fbd87aee2c4b19b7",
      "audioDurationSec": 17.475918,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-04-after.779293c3.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 5.720816,
      "afterTextHash": "779293c3226067281e306035078417a856f700a6a99f8cf11f0268fe011beb7b"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-05",
      "markerIndex": 4,
      "replayStartSec": 25.737687,
      "replayEndSec": 32.972076,
      "narrationText": "忘记了值？别去偷看，轮换它。rotate-secret 标志会跳过前置条件检查，审计日志将此次变更标记为有意为之的轮换操作，明确、清晰、安全。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-05.bb39a8fc.mp3",
      "textHash": "bb39a8fcd6c7bef182ed78d5e2d106e41b9981d45b97f8d487ba99223f149d2c",
      "audioDurationSec": 16.43102,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-05-after.c7a64d0c.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.519184,
      "afterTextHash": "c7a64d0c116157091f18e30313b27c811f7d24c629938a411b88a7a1e27c3954"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-06",
      "markerIndex": 5,
      "replayStartSec": 32.972076,
      "replayEndSec": 39.065377,
      "narrationText": "现在是重头戏。让我们 fork 这个仓库。fork 是父仓库加密镜像的逐字节拷贝。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-06.e5e85dce.mp3",
      "textHash": "e5e85dcee912cdc8e3780aa5e5a4111fbbf500bdde2aa833157d92e4ea1b659e",
      "audioDurationSec": 7.549388,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-06-after.8a2ce789.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.317551,
      "afterTextHash": "8a2ce7894a224ac3ecc566a4a6c9da6aad89543fb74deb6a9292971208f7cb8f"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-managing-secrets-07",
      "markerIndex": 6,
      "replayStartSec": 39.065377,
      "replayEndSec": 44.3362,
      "narrationText": "但当我们列出 fork 的密钥时，是空的。没有 Stripe 密钥，没有数据库密码，没有 API 令牌。fork 无法伪装成你，这就是「克隆生产环境，万无一失」真正奏效的原因。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-07.d0e05da0.mp3",
      "textHash": "d0e05da034ed5c0309494c7346b2e4aa44dfbf0d3f1d6a75d09c1c71f312ae0b",
      "audioDurationSec": 28.995918,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/tutorial-managing-secrets-07-after.e191b125.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.474286,
      "afterTextHash": "e191b125cbf4193a94aa97101293345c81906f06844a387e62ca534d7595c111"
    }
  ],
  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "textHash": "d40d7382d19e84804baf712ccc9470561f37cca752bd3e895a0410d8c203bfb9",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/intro.d40d7382.mp3",
      "narrationText": "是时候把真正的凭据放到 fork 触不到的地方了！我们会设置两个密钥，证明它们是只写的，然后 fork 仓库，看着它们消失。",
      "audioDurationSec": 11.075918
    },
    {
      "id": "env-trap",
      "textHash": "5572853f9c7d2241acb0c52a680fbbfe064138cb11b26ee2cf9842ca64dd225d",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/env-trap.5572853f.mp3",
      "narrationText": "大多数团队会把一个 .env 文件丢进仓库，因为这是最直接的做法。问题在于 fork 会继承镜像的逐字节拷贝，于是你的沙箱启动时就带着生产环境的 Stripe 密钥，开始向真实客户的银行卡扣款。",
      "audioDurationSec": 19.722449
    },
    {
      "id": "write-only",
      "textHash": "8609a1c36fa40fe1cc4e7451ecde27f8634a7781e656b4f72da16799ef9e681b",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/write-only.8609a1c3.mp3",
      "narrationText": "CLI 遵循 GitHub Actions 模型：get 返回的是摘要，而非值。如果你弄丢了某个密钥，不要去偷看，去轮换它，审计日志会将这次操作记录为一次有意的变更。",
      "audioDurationSec": 15.725714
    },
    {
      "id": "fork-isolation",
      "textHash": "881e49d9bfb0bfecbbd6ff87dc02bd6608b2cbb13610c830164f011c95ef3003",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/fork-isolation.881e49d9.mp3",
      "narrationText": "这就是回报。fork 共享父仓库的加密数据，但密钥存储按 repo 划分作用域，所以 fork 列出来是空的，无法插入任何你的生产密钥。",
      "audioDurationSec": 14.445714
    },
    {
      "id": "next-tutorial",
      "textHash": "d290c7550ee53735b4ffa8938938f2775d491d400b3c3534406895a835ba4224",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-managing-secrets/next-tutorial.d290c755.mp3",
      "narrationText": "密钥就这样被锁在 fork 跟不到的地方了。下个教程见！",
      "audioDurationSec": 5.32898
    }
  ]
}
